high_descs: Turn left. Exit the room. When you reach the fridge, turn left. Then turn right until you are next to the high shelf. Turn left.
Open the upper doors of the shelf. Take the ladle. Close the doors.
Turn around. Move a little and turn left. Approach the sink.
Place the ladle on the left side of the sink cabinet.
Turn around, go to the countertop where the microwave is. Turn left.
Grab the ladle.
Turn around. Move a little. Turn to the right. Reach the sink.
Place the ladle perpendicularly on top of the other.
anns.task_desc: Find two ladles. Place them on the sink cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the fridge in the kitchen.
Open the fridge and pick up the ladle inside.
Turn left and approach the kitchen sink.
Set the ladle down to the left of the sink.
Turn right and walk up to the countertop right of the microwave.
Pick up the ladle from the counter
Turn left and walk back to the sink.
Set the ladle down to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the ladle on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take the ladle from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the ladle on the sink table.
Turn around and go near the countertop.
Take another ladle on the oven table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the ladle on the sink table.
anns.task_desc: Collect the ladle and place it on the sink.
